;; Real, ToS-compliant source list for web/collect.cljs.
;;
;; Each entry is one company's OWN official job board, hosted on
;; Greenhouse's public Job Board API
;; (https://developers.greenhouse.io/job-board.html) -- documented,
;; unauthenticated, read-only, published by Greenhouse specifically for
;; external aggregation/embedding. No scraping, no bot-detection
;; evasion, no ToS violation: every employer listed here has already
;; chosen to expose its own postings this way.
;;
;;   :board  -- the Greenhouse board token, i.e. the <token> in
;;              https://boards-api.greenhouse.io/v1/boards/<token>/jobs
;;   :source -- provenance tag written onto every posting this board
;;              produces (jobsearchops posting-record field). All
;;              entries here are "employer-direct": Greenhouse-hosted
;;              boards ARE each company's own official careers site,
;;              not a third-party republication requiring source
;;              consent.
;;
;; Add/remove companies by editing this file -- collect.cljs has no
;; hardcoded company list. Verified live (real, currently-open
;; postings observed) on 2026-07-24: carvana carries genuine hourly-
;; wage-disclosed US roles, figma carries a real Tokyo (JPN) listing,
;; gitlab/reddit/pinterest carry real EU (GBR/DEU/FRA) listings.
[{:board "carvana" :source "employer-direct"}
 {:board "figma" :source "employer-direct"}
 {:board "gitlab" :source "employer-direct"}
 {:board "reddit" :source "employer-direct"}
 {:board "pinterest" :source "employer-direct"}]
